                    <br><br>
                    <i class="icofont-star-alt-1 text-naranja"></i> Perform reports and apply the proper methodologies to make the project moves on
                    <br><br>
                    <i class="icofont-star-alt-1 text-naranja"></i>	Provide outstanding customer service prior, during, and post project delivery
